Teltoli winces and shakes her legs, panthers with wings really weren't made for holding heavy raptors through the air. She activates her com link and speaks to both Carnage and Cyber Claw. 

:: See ya round guys, and do good in the battle. Teltoli out ::

She sighs and her quick eyes look up, spotting any Predacons she could attack from the sky. There was Megatron, at least that's who she thought it was. There was.. Dinobot? The Raptor wouldn' have much impersonating him now!!

The flying Panther/Hawk picked out Scourge, and gave a screeching roar! She folds her wings into a dive and zooms up behind him, aiming for his back to tackle him to the ground where she could then pulls out her energon swords and get ready for battle!
